Title: ' The secret history of Quinta da Regaleira'
DateModified: '2019-02-19'
DatePublished: '2019-02-19'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-secret-history-of-quinta-da-regaleira
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Adriana Navarro Ramirez
AuthorCountry: Mexico
Text: The myths and legends that are told around the Quinta da Regaleria. The history
  of the place. The characters that inhabited the house. About its construction. The
  parties that were held there. The rites of initiation. And the current stories that
  are told about the place.
